thread.title: Maris Freimanis

author: Maris Freimanis
title: Maris Freimanis
text:
We booked Citroen Cactus two weeks before arrival to Gran Canaria and there was no payment or credit card details needed to made reservation. No queues at the desk and after 5min we already got the keys. 90eur for 6 days with 0eur excess insurance and free child seats. And guess what, we get what we booked - brand new Cactus with just 2000km mileage. Came back at 6am and just drop the keys in the box.
Best overall experience with car rentals.
